com.worldpay

Interface WorldpayResponse


  • public interface WorldpayResponse
    Developers have to implement this interface in order to handle response from Worldpay#createTokenAsyncTask(android.content.Context, Card, WorldpayResponse) or Worldpay#createTokenAsyncTask(android.content.Context, ResponseCard, WorldpayResponse).
    See Also:
    ResponseCard, ResponseError, WorldpayError
